Package ohos.aafwk.ability.delegation

Interface IAbilityDelegatorArgs


  • public interface IAbilityDelegatorArgs
    Stores unit testing-related parameters, including the class loader, test case names, and test runner name.

    You can call AbilityDelegatorRegistry#getArguments to obtain an IAbilityDelegatorArgs object.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Aafwk#ABILITY
